channel.title: Kihomura's 317 client 2.0
channel.description:
[center]Kihomura's 317 client 2.0[/center]
[b]Features[/b]
Fixed the ints on some of the items so they look more realistic Simple 417 gameframe Very shitty censor, but keeps advertisers away... kind of. Added a new compass to the client. (?...) As far as I know, there is no models that have been overwritten (Such as a fence turning into a Helm of Neitiznot.) Fixed Dragonfire shield. Very basic client, will work on most servers that are configured for Miss Silabsoft's client. Nothing really 'fancy' went into this client.
Note: I still have quite a few item ints to fix, but it shouldn't take too long.
Picture...
[img]http://i40.tinypic.com/288auee.png[/img]
That's pretty much the entire client summed up into one picture.
[url=http://files.filefront.com/Kihomuras+clientzip/;12893849;/fileinfo.html]Download here[/url]
[size=8pt][i]Also be on the lookout for my extremely sexy server that's coming out. U-Rune.[/i][/size]
[center]Credits Jagex, GalkonsPride, `Rich, ~google~[/center]
